title: MILLION DOLLAZ WORTH OF GAME EP: 100 "BILLION DOLLAZ WORTH OF GAME" FEATURING DA BABY
description:
Wallo and Gillie went down to Charlotte to interview Grammy nominated rapper, Da Baby for their special 100th episode of Million Dollaz Worth of Game.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/mworthofgame
